If an animal is a dog, it must have four legs. Therefore, having four legs is not sufficient proof that it is a dog; it is only a necessary condition.
To bake a cake, flour is necessary. If you omit the flour, the cake cannot exist. Therefore, flour is a fundamental prerequisite for this recipe.
