You should schedule a follow-up appointment in two weeks. We need to reassess the inflammation levels and adjust your medication dosage accordingly.
While recovery is expected, you need to gradually increase your physical activity over the coming weeks, starting with light walking only.
I recommend a dietary change focusing on anti-inflammatory foods. This lifestyle adjustment is crucial for improving your long-term prognosis.
