Strategic logistical planning involved mapping out the entire supply chain, anticipating fuel consumption rates, ammunition expenditure, and medical evacuation requirements for weeks of continuous operation. Engineers meticulously calculated the necessary infrastructure support, including forward operating bases and reinforced supply depots.
